snippet: Having spent a large chunk of last year as the world's number one ranked golfer, it was no surprise to see Jordan Spieth's name at the top of the leaderboard at any tournament where he chose to tee it up....
lead_paragraph: Having spent a large chunk of last year as the world's number one ranked golfer, it was no surprise to see Jordan Spieth's name at the top of the leaderboard at any tournament where he chose to tee it up.

headline.main: Spieth Cashes In, but at What Price?
headline.print_headline: Spieth Cashes In, but at What Price?
